name: A road #1. (The place where you were supposed to die.)
description:
jpeg, 1080 x 810px., 2021. From the series "In Absentia" by x3r0ne

"In Absentia" is a photographic series where the subject matter has been removed digitally leaving a space feeling off and even sometimes completely empty. Scenes of action reduced to the banal of the everyday. What is missing? Why is it gone?
